{"tid":1535710,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你 香港人爭下氣 跳閘啦好嗎？","createTime":"2019-09-03T12:48:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T10:15:53.000Z","uid":314130,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7932f33d7445b1b2147773b510bbe01b472ec1ed","tid":1535710,"uid":314130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T12:48:08.000Z","msg":"屌你老味<br />\n<br />\n今日頭先晏晝諗住跳閘嗰時，一行入去黨鐵站<br />\n就見到一大班港豬乖乖地排隊比錢搭車<br />\n又唔係用綠卡<br />\n幾十人 好多後生 冇一個敢跳<br />\n開初以為有便衣喺隔離伏9人佢哋先唔敢跳<br />\n一望發現附近十里乜人都冇 <br />\n得一個黃衫喺客務中心 一眼都無撚望過部閘機<br />\n最後得我自己一個跳<br />\n出閘亦都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">爭氣啦，香港人</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">721 831係咪仲唔夠認清黨鐵呀 近乎零手尾跟都唔做？ 仲想送錢比班仆街？</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>懇請各位香港人由今日起跳閘過 唔好再比錢搭黨鐵 <br />\n最低限度都請用綠卡 蝕到佢仆街！！！</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔識就睇呢條片:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pLjuuYOyhk8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpLjuuYOyhk8&d=wLht58ApaBOsBOdSjqbSDZgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=7dd0c849\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pLjuuYOyhk8</a>"},{"pid":"23b02b0a42a31872e2e49cbd03f8d8778820eaa9","tid":1535710,"uid":153722,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T12:50:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">比狗打 比狗虐待 黨鐵pk?<br />\n我地玩跳閘報復先 yeah<br />\n好叻呀我成功令黨鐵賺少我幾十蚊呀</span>"},{"pid":"cfce5a64e4553b2d2f764e386151ac5219653018","tid":1535710,"uid":267263,"like"